---
title: Sweet Soy Pulled Pork & Green Beans with Jasmine Rice, Sriracha Aioli & Peanuts
description: When it comes to the rice bowl, you know us: we love to throw together all the textures and flavors for so many delicious combinations. Our chefs took it up a notch with tonight’s sweet soy glazed pull pork (texture #1), tender green beans (#2), fluffy jasmine rice (#3), crunchy peanuts (#4), and creamy Sriracha mayo (#5). We did the math, and that’s five flavors and textures that are sure make one un-bowl-ievable dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-soy-pulled-pork-green-beans-00e33759.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/sweet-soy-pulled-pork-green-beans-615dba8eea306d1abc41107d-b991f460.pdf
cuisine: Asian
